---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="个人简介" description="Amy 的个人主页">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">HELLO, WORLD</p>
      <h1>你好，我是 <span>Amy</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">
        一名对人工智能与软件开发保持好奇的学生。这里记录我的学习、项目，
        以及偶尔冒出来的想法。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button primary" href="/blog/">阅读博客 <span>→</span></a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://github.com/Amy22707" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub ↗</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-card">
      <img src="/avatar.jpg" alt="Amy 的头像" />
      <div>
        <strong>Amy</strong>
        <span>Student · Developer</span>
      </div>
      <p>📍 Beijing, China</p>
      <p>🎓 Peking University</p>
      <p>💡 AI · Python · Web</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">ABOUT ME</p>
        <h2>关于我</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <article class="info-card">
        <span class="card-icon">01</span>
        <h3>我在学习</h3>
        <p>人工智能、机器学习与计算机科学。最近正在完成中国标准麻将 AI 项目。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="info-card">
        <span class="card-icon">02</span>
        <h3>我在创造</h3>
        <p>把课堂知识变成真正可以运行的代码，也把踩过的坑整理成博客。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="info-card">
        <span class="card-icon">03</span>
        <h3>我喜欢</h3>
        <p>清晰的表达、漂亮而克制的设计，以及从零到一完成一个作品。</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
